{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-introducing-yourself/task-8","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 8","description":"","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pronađi tačnu reč iz liste ispod da bi dovršio uvod za Juliju.</p>\n<p><strong>VAŽNO:</strong> Neke reči se ne koriste, druge nemaju smisla u ovom kontekstu, i možete koristiti svaku reč <strong>samo jednom</strong>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">estratega</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uruguayo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uruguaya</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mañana</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">treinta y seis</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">científico</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Perú</span></p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Estratega</span> odgovara izreci <span class=\"highlighted-text\">estratega de marketing</span>, opisujući profesiju Julije.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Uruguaya</span> je ženski narod koji odgovara zemlji Julije.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y seis</span> Ovo je starost Julijete.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mañana</span> završavaš sa opaskama <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta mañana</span>.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-practice-introducing-yourself","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-introducing-yourself/task-8"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Hola, me llamo Julieta.</p>\n<p>Soy BLANK de marketing.</p>\n<p>Soy de Uruguay, soy BLANK.</p>\n<p>Tengo BLANK años. Hasta BLANK.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"estratega","feedback":"<p>Pronađi reč koja odgovara struci povezanoj sa marketingom.</p>"},{"answer":"uruguaya","feedback":